					<div class="glass-panel tensegrity-widget-container">
						<p class="bio-text" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
							Interactive simulation of the structural system. Drag the floating modules to observe how tension lines distribute compression load forces throughout the three-tiered suspended profile.
						</p>
						<div class="widget-canvas-container">
							<canvas id="tensegrityCanvas" class="widget-canvas"></canvas>
						</div>
						<div class="widget-controls">
							<span>Drag node nodes to pull strings • Double click to reset</span>
